  "instructions": [
    "Heat a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and minced garlic to the pan, cooking until soft and fragrant.",
    "Stir in the fermented green beans with their liquid, and cook for about 2 minutes.",
    "In another small bowl, mix cornstarch with a little water to form a slurry.",
    "Slowly pour in the almond milk while continuously whisking to avoid lumps. Add low-sodium soy sauce and water or broth. Bring to a simmer and let it thicken slightly.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions before serving.",
